observationText: The QGP-1 cell line showed strong staining for neuron-specific enolase (NSE), moderate staining for CD57, and weak staining for the neuroendocrine markers VMAT1 and 5-HT.
The QGP-1 cell line exhibited weak to moderate staining for the epithelial markers cytokeratin 8/18, confirming its epithelial phenotype.
